javac.util

类 StringUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • javac.util.StringUtils

  • public class StringUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of utilities for String manipulation.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

    • 方法详细资料

      • toLowerCase

        public static java.lang.String toLowerCase(java.lang.String source)
        Converts the given String to lower case using the US Locale. The result is independent of the default Locale in the current JVM instance.

      • toUpperCase

        public static java.lang.String toUpperCase(java.lang.String source)
        Converts the given String to upper case using the US Locale. The result is independent of the default Locale in the current JVM instance.

      • indexOfIgnoreCase

        public static int indexOfIgnoreCase(java.lang.String text,
                                    java.lang.String str)
        Case insensitive version of String.indexOf(String). Equivalent to text.indexOf(str), except the matching is case insensitive.

      • indexOfIgnoreCase

        public static int indexOfIgnoreCase(java.lang.String text,
                                    java.lang.String str,
                                    int startIndex)
        Case insensitive version of String.indexOf(String, int). Equivalent to text.indexOf(str, startIndex), except the matching is case insensitive.
